WIZARD

  The `ai wizard` command initiates interactive or non-interactive wizard
  walk thrus for various AI services and tools.

  To try it out:
                                                                                                                                        
    TRY: ai wizard     

USAGE: ai wizard [...]

  AZURE
    --subscription SUBSCRIPTION   (see: ai help wizard subscription)

  RESOURCE
    --region REGION               (see: ai help wizard region)
    --group GROUP                 (see: ai help wizard group)
    --name NAME                   (see: ai help wizard name)

  CHAT
    --model MODEL                 (see: ai help wizard model)
    --deployment DEPLOYMENT       (see: ai help wizard deployment)
    --system PROMPT               (see: ai help wizard system prompt)

  INPUT                           (see: ai help wizard input)
    --file FILE                   (see: ai help wizard file)
    --files PATTERN               (see: ai help wizard files)
    --files @FILELIST.txt         (see: ai help wizard files)
    --jsonl FILE                  (see: ai help wizard jsonl)

SEE ALSO

  ai help wizard advanced
  ai help wizard examples
  ai help find topics wizard